1. alsa.conf

	$ sudo sh -c "printf 'pcm.0.card 0 pcm.0.device 0 pcm.0.subdevice 0 pcm.0.type hw defaults.pcm.minperiodtime 2772    ;  ' > /usr/share/alsa/alsa.conf.min"

2. Config files

	mpd.conf, upmpdcli.conf, mympd.conf, roon

	$ sudo nano *.conf (mpd, upmpdcli, mympd, roon, spotifyd)
	quadruple-space+line feed+double-space at the end without new line

3. Strip debug

	libasound, libaudiofile, libFLAC, mpd, librespot

	$ file /usr/bin/mpd /usr/bin/librespot /usr/lib/.../libasound.so.2.0.0.min{n,x}
	$ sudo strip --strip-debug /usr/bin/mpd /usr/bin/librespot /usr/lib/.../libasound.so.2.0.0.min{n,x}

4. Build libaudiofile & libFLAC

5. Disable systemd-journald & systemd-logind

	$ sudo systemctl mask systemd-journald.service systemd-journald.socket systemd-journald-audit.service systemd-journald-audit.socket systemd-journald-dev-log.socket systemd-journal-flush
	$ sudo systemctl mask systemd-logind

6. Improve blacklist & cpu affinity for artik710
